{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  </div><div class=\"p\">AUTORIZA EMISOR DE DOCUMENTOS TRIBUTARIOS ELECTR&#xD3;NICOS</div></div>", "i": 9373509}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Extracto de resoluci&#xF3;n exenta del Servicio de Impuestos Internos N&#xBA; 79, de 30 de agosto de 2013, que autoriza a contribuyentes como emisores de documentos tributarios electr&#xF3;nicos y boletas electr&#xF3;nicas.</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Se autoriza como emisor de documentos tributarios electr&#xF3;nicos a contribuyentes: RUT 76.078.544-K, RUT 99.581.960-0, RUT 76.296.942-4, RUT 86.882.500-6, RUT 79.811.120-5, RUT 76.735.900-4, RUT 76.025.259-K, RUT 76.229.620-9, RUT 77.834.700-8, RUT 76.218.919-4, RUT 76.261.409-K, RUT 76.162.983-2, RUT 83.187.800-2, RUT 12.056.669-5, RUT 76.936.000-K, RUT 16.460.037-8, RUT 52.004.364-0, RUT 89.524.800-2, RUT 76.044.977-6, RUT 11.331.569-5, RUT 76.178.352-1, RUT 12.868.930-3, RUT 77.095.540-8, RUT 76.110.044-0, RUT 76.291.607-K, RUT 77.319.660-5, RUT 96.546.910-9, RUT 76.278.048-8, RUT 76.127.343-4, RUT 79.849.190-3, RUT 76.256.114-K, RUT 76.033.634-3, RUT 76.047.265-4, RUT 76.221.834-8, RUT 76.278.348-7, RUT 96.955.280-9, RUT 76.057.013-3, RUT 76.176.469-1, RUT 76.262.083-9, RUT 77.472.420-6, RUT 76.274.681-6, RUT 99.502.980-4, RUT 96.843.710-0, RUT 96.751.940-5, RUT 76.241.093-1, RUT 76.269.234-1, RUT 77.023.940-0, RUT 96.947.020-9, RUT 76.263.108-3, RUT 76.110.985-5, RUT 88.450.000-1, RUT 76.233.613-8, RUT 18.169.903-5, RUT 99.552.660-3, RUT 76.154.079-3, RUT 79.778.640-3, RUT 76.412.790-0, RUT 96.962.050-2, RUT 96.828.120-8, RUT 76.213.387-3, RUT 76.142.721-0, RUT 76.200.116-0, RUT 76.259.511-7, RUT 76.263.288-8, RUT 78.824.220-4, RUT 77.244.240-8, RUT 76.273.260-2, RUT 76.289.336-3, RUT 76.205.592-9, RUT 76.189.561-3, RUT 76.616.420-K, RUT 76.027.389-9, RUT 96.757.960-2, RUT 76.043.077-3, RUT 96.824.450-7, RUT 76.033.